headline: FedEx opens dedicated freight facility at UK airport

headline: Why Sprout Social (SPT) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of social media management platform Sprout Social (NASDAQ:SPT) jumped 2.8% in the afternoon session after Needham reiterated its Buy rating on the stock, highlighting the company's new integration with design platform Canva as a positive catalyst.
